            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指開跌113點或0.44%，報25350，低水151點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">科指期貨開跌54點或1.08%，報4938，低水58點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國指貨開升1點或0.01%，報8688，低水8點。</p>\n</div>",
